{"tid":617453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呃WhatsApp驗證碼　騙徒盜賬號詐財","createTime":"2018-04-05T03:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T02:54:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3f2c462394f14495ef65ff5c87c90bdc045c7b64","tid":617453,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T03:37:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180405/20352770\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F20352770&d=zc069oswvsp2mKSTV1okGywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=92b8e8ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F20352770&h=8c9cf728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180405/20352770</a><br />\n<br />\n呃WhatsApp驗證碼　騙徒盜賬號詐財<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】騙徒經常以「白撞」方式騙取受害人WhatsApp賬號，再向其朋友行騙。近日流傳的一段錄音中，有人稱有幾位朋友的電話被入侵，受害人收到某位友人訊息，稱會向他發送一個含有4位數或6位數號碼的電話訊息，並要求他覆述，但該組數字其實是WhatsApp賬號的驗證碼，騙徒取得驗證碼，即重啟賬號並假扮成受害人，詐騙其電話簿中的朋友，例如要求購買點數卡。<br />\n<br />\n電話騙案時有發生，近日流傳的一段錄音中，有人指有幾位朋友因覆述WhatsApp驗證碼而「中招」，呼籲朋友不要回覆有關訊息，「總之幾熟都好，老竇老母叫你睇個訊息，個訊息係6個冧巴，或者4個冧巴，叫你覆一次俾佢聽，你就唔好覆佢喇」。<br />\n<br />\n電視節目《東張西望》早前訪問了一名苦主伍小姐，騙徒盜取其WhatsApp賬號後，便向其電話簿聯絡人行騙，每人各被騙去1,280元。<br />\n<br />\n而上月初網上已流傳一張通告，稱由警方發出，指荃灣警區內有多宗以「白撞」形式要求事主提供驗證碼個案，如受害人不小心交出，騙徒便會利用其聯絡人資料，要求其友人購買點數卡。<br />\n<br />\n香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑表示，透過「白撞」形式騙取賬號是最常見和最簡單的方法，建議開啟WhatsApp和即時通訊軟件的二步驗證碼，會較只用短訊傳送的驗證碼安全，不要開啟或下載不明來歷的連結和軟件，並為電話安裝及更新防毒軟件。<br />\n<br />\n■記者曾偉龍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180405/large/a05a01a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180405%2Flarge%2Fa05a01a.gif&h=ccaac328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日流傳的一段錄音中，有人指有幾位朋友因覆述WhatsApp驗證碼「中招」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實咩原理 ？<br />\n點樣呃驗證碼 ？"},{"pid":"9fd05f80e7a410e0e87fe3e9ac55e047823d9513","tid":617453,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"其實點解一定要買點數卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdddfe1d6ba9560c3928f74e46bb9db1f7a8a29","tid":617453,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"呢段只係冇採訪嘅舊聞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e038b4c746dc0ea7e0cc95e0a3ad94c03b9e57fc","tid":617453,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:19:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e086d75ae46bb571e2079daf8871f5664cda4a2a","tid":617453,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9fd05f80e7a410e0e87fe3e9ac55e047823d9513","tid":617453,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"其實點解一定要買點數卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:19:18.000Z","msg":"經第三方手難追，可以幾10個銀行account + 幾10 個網上account<br />\n<br />\n點數係商品，同貨幣唔同。有d 點數可以直接變錢，有d 就通過不同賣買變返錢<br />\n<br />\n目的都係唔想人查到。"},{"pid":"9dad0ed1fe7f3e27270d7b84368a47d097a01eb2","tid":617453,"uid":113408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fd05f80e7a410e0e87fe3e9ac55e047823d9513","tid":617453,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"其實點解一定要買點數卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:24:20.000Z","msg":"唔通比自己個銀行戶口叫佢入錢入去咩"},{"pid":"b84be26e2f3c4e3267224a8052963c5f24d53e5d","tid":617453,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T